# Apple Magic User-Mode Service Scaffold

This folder will contain the user-mode service / console harness.

Initial Roadmap:
1. Device discovery using SetupDi / CM APIs for GUID_DEVINTERFACE_APPLE_MAGIC_RAW.
2. Periodic IOCTL_APPLE_MAGIC_PARSE_LAST requests to driver.
3. Logging parsed deltas / buttons to console.
4. Gesture recognizer (state machine) abstraction.
5. Injection backend abstraction (SendInput vs VHF virtual dev).
6. Convert to Windows Service (ServiceMain, HandlerEx) + config file.

Not yet implemented.
